ontent":{"data":"▼概要<br>「Reflection Board」は、登壇者と参加者がいっしょに創り上げる掲示板型コンテンツです。メインステージに登壇するスピーカーから掲示された「問い」への応答をReflection Boardに貼ってみることで、普段の仕事ではなかなか考えない「デザイナーとしての自己」を見つめ直す機会を得ることができます。また他者の「応答」を眺めることで多様な考えと出会うことも。「聞く」だけでなく、「考える」Designshipの楽しみを提供します。<br><br>▼場所<br>Meetup Area @B1F ホワイエB<br><br>▼参加方法<br>お好きな時間にお越しください。<br>","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"@mobile":{"fontSize":"12px"},"color":"#FFFFFF","flex":"none","fontFamily":"var(--s-font-b480a875)","fontSize":"14px","fontWeight":700,"height":"auto","letterSpacing":"0.06em","lineHeight":"2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","textAlign":"left","width":"100%"},"tagName":"","uuid":"5af9d687-9963-4ff4-bc17-8273dbdccae9","children":[]}],"name":"<group>","style":{"@mobile":{"flex":"none","padding":"32px 20px 32px 20px","width":"92%"},"@tablet":{"flex":"none","width":"820px"},"alignContent":"flex-start","alignItems":"flex-start","background":"rgb(45, 48, 64)","flex":"none","flexDirection":"column","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"flex-start","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","padding":"32px","width":"820px"},"tagName":"div","uuid":"648caafd-35d8-49bb-a4e3-87adfa3ef3c4"},{"children":[{"content":{"data":"Speaker’s Circle | スピーカーと対話してみよう","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"@mini":{"fontSize":"24px"},"@mobile":{"fontSize":"24px"},"color":"#FFFFFF","flex":"none","fontFamily":"var(--s-font-b480a875)","fontSize":"32px","fontWeight":700,"height":"auto","letterSpacing":"0.06em","lineHeight":"1.4","margin":"0px 0px 24px 0px","textAlign":"left","width":"100%"},"tagName":"h3","uuid":"28b7b067-9956-4331-b9e9-3641a38a73df","children":[]},{"content":{"data":"▼概要<br>「Speaker's Circle」は、メインステージでのスピーチ直後にキーノートスピーカーや公募スピーカーと直接対話できる参加型ミニセッションです。スピーカーが提示する「問い」をテーマに、ファシリテーターが対話を導きます。デザインの視点から刺激的な議論を交わし、少人数だからこそ生まれる濃密なコミュニケーションを通じて、新たなインスピレーションを得られる場となっています。<br><br>▼場所<br>Meetup Area @B1F ホワイエB<br>Reflection Board前<br><br>▼参加方法<br>以下の時間に、ホワイエBのReflection Board前にお越しください。<br><br>▼参加スピーカー<br>Day1：<br>・塩月 慶子 / 橋田 規子（15:40-16:10）<br>・朝山 絵美 / Brandon K. Hill （17:30-18:00）<br>・引地 耕太（19:00-19:20）<br>Day2：<br>・菅 俊一（13:40-14:00）<br>・宮城 愛彦 / 東郷 りん（15:30-16:00）<br>・鈴木 啓太（17:20-17:40）<br>・菅野 薫（19:00-19:20）<br>","type":"text"},"name":"Text","style":{"@mobile":{"fontSize":"12px"},"color":"#FFFFFF","flex":"none","fontFamily":"var(--s-font-b480a875)","fontSize":"14px","fontWeight":700,"height":"auto","letterSpacing":"0.06em","lineHeight":"2","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","textAlign":"left","width":"100%"},"tagName":"","uuid":"f8a1edd3-32ce-47e6-9cf5-86eb99e8b320","children":[]}],"name":"<group>","style":{"@mobile":{"flex":"none","padding":"32px 20px 32px 20px","width":"92%"},"@tablet":{"flex":"none","width":"820px"},"alignContent":"flex-start","alignItems":"flex-start","background":"rgb(45, 48, 64)","flex":"none","flexDirection":"column","flexWrap":"nowrap","justifyContent":"flex-start","margin":"0px 0px 0px 0px","padding":"32px","width":"820px"},"tagName":"div","uuid":"f23ab781-f7f7-438f-a8b1-18d0760a74e4"}],"name":"<group>","style":{"@tablet":{"alignContent":"center","alignItems":"center","justifyContent":"flex-start","padding":"0px 16px 0px 16px"},"alignContent":"center","alignItems":"center","flexWrap":"nowrap","gap":"40px","justifyContent":"center","padding":"0px"},"tagName":"div","uuid":"c7593cdd-65f6-4b7d-890b-677498a72fbe"}],"content":{"data":"","type":""},"id":"meetup","name":"Section","style":{"@mobile":{"justifyContent":"flex-start","margin":"80px 0px 0px 0px","overflowY":"auto","padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},"@small":{"padding":"0px 0px 41px 0px"},"@tablet":{"padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px"},"background":"#1b1d28","borderRadius":"0px","margin":"48px 0px 0px 0px","opacity":1,"overflowX":"visible","overflowY":"visible","padding":"0px 0px 0px 0px","width":"100%"},"uuid":"49bf33dd-c62a-4ddc-ad78-9523bdc23d22"},{"type":"ref","refId":"3209728d-7886-4f56-b02b-e52d4354ae98"},{"children":[{"attrs":{"target":"_blank"},"children":[{"content":{"data":"&nbsp;参加登録（無料）<br>","type":"text"},"name":"button","style":{"@mobile":{"flex":"none"